1
00:01:32,340 --> 00:01:35,020
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:37,940
[Episode 13]

3
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:04,730
I'm sorry

4
00:02:05,590 --> 00:02:06,150
I'm late.

5
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,880
If I had gone to see her one last time

6
00:02:11,590 --> 00:02:13,590
and talked things through with her,

7
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,150
Mei wouldn't have...

8
00:02:16,150 --> 00:02:17,810
No one can predict the future.

9
00:02:18,310 --> 00:02:19,860
You didn't do anything wrong.

10
00:02:18,710 --> 00:02:19,710
♪ Tell me ♪

11
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:23,870
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

12
00:02:25,430 --> 00:02:26,579
♪ Walk past me ♪

13
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:30,710
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

14
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:29,079
I'm so useless.

15
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:34,110
Why am I so useless?

16
00:02:31,970 --> 00:02:34,500
♪ Don't watch me as the rain falls ♪

17
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:38,140
♪ Love burns too hot as it passes ♪

18
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,110
You're just human.

19
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:44,620
♪ Even a lifetime of war
cannot be extinguished ♪

20
00:02:43,230 --> 00:02:44,360
It must hurt, right?

21
00:02:45,740 --> 00:02:46,829
♪ Blame me ♪

22
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:48,310
Even though she was just a 2D character,

23
00:02:47,530 --> 00:02:50,990
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

24
00:02:49,070 --> 00:02:50,670
you've known her for so long.

25
00:02:52,579 --> 00:02:53,650
♪ Hide me ♪

26
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:54,310
I know how much she means to you.

27
00:02:54,130 --> 00:02:58,180
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

28
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,440
It's okay.

29
00:02:59,579 --> 00:03:01,940
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

30
00:02:59,930 --> 00:03:00,920
Cry if you want.

31
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:05,430
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

32
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:03,560
I'm here.

33
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:09,240
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

34
00:03:09,260 --> 00:03:11,420
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

35
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:14,270
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

36
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:16,079
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

37
00:03:16,110 --> 00:03:18,630
♪ I never yielded ♪

38
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:20,380
♪ But why ♪

39
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:25,170
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

40
00:03:25,570 --> 00:03:27,940
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

41
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:29,829
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

42
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,680
I'm sorry.

43
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:32,240
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

44
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:31,760
That day on the lake,

45
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,360
♪ The first time I met you ♪

46
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,150
I shouldn't have suspected you of
staging the whole thing yourself.

47
00:03:34,730 --> 00:03:37,910
♪ There was once light ♪

48
00:03:38,470 --> 00:03:46,829
♪ In my soul ♪

49
00:03:38,880 --> 00:03:39,560
It's okay.

50
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:43,850
I know you were scared.

51
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:47,920
I didn't think things through.

52
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,700
Give me a little more time.

53
00:03:51,920 --> 00:03:53,280
I'll try to adapt.

54
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:55,450
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

55
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,130
You don't have to adapt.

56
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:57,260
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

57
00:03:57,290 --> 00:03:59,810
♪ I never yielded ♪

58
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,120
From now on, if there's ever
danger like this again,

59
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,640
♪ But why ♪

60
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:03,000
or anything that requires
getting your hands dirty,

61
00:04:01,850 --> 00:04:06,410
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

62
00:04:04,860 --> 00:04:05,790
let me handle it.

63
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:09,110
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

64
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:09,560
Why?

65
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:11,010
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

66
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,010
Did you forget?

67
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:13,420
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

68
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:13,630
I'm an actor.

69
00:04:13,780 --> 00:04:15,570
♪ The first time I met you ♪

70
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:17,240
I can play any role

71
00:04:16,130 --> 00:04:24,030
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

72
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:19,040
without psychological burden.

73
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:23,950
And you—

74
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,960
you never have to change.

75
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:47,159
Maid Mei's assassination attempt
on Consort Shu was exposed.

76
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:49,720
Concubine Yu had a fierce quarrel
with His Majesty,

77
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:52,430
and in a fit of anger, His Majesty
consigned her to the Cold Palace.

78
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:54,430
But instead of admitting her fault,

79
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:57,000
Concubine Yu urged His Majesty
to get rid of Consort Shu,

80
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,070
claiming

81
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,650
she had dreamt that Consort Shu

82
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:04,100
would one day kill her entire family.

83
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:07,510
Dreamt?

84
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:10,190
Of course His Majesty didn't believe her.

85
00:05:10,190 --> 00:05:13,430
He rebuked Concubine Yu for making
jealous, baseless claims to gain favor.

86
00:05:13,430 --> 00:05:14,230
Your Majesty.

87
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,870
If Consort Shu's family hadn't
plotted against my father first,

88
00:05:16,870 --> 00:05:18,480
Mei would never have tried to
assassinate her for no reason.

89
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,810
How dare you argue back!

90
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:21,560
I've been too lenient with you—

91
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:23,270
that you dare behave so outrageously!

92
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:25,160
Why won't Your Majesty believe me?

93
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:25,620
Shut up!

94
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:28,040
You will stay here
and reflect on your actions.

95
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,840
Your Majesty!

96
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,410
-Nail the doors and windows shut,
-Your Majesty!

97
00:05:30,410 --> 00:05:31,740
[Office of Drums and Bells]

98
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,270
and post guards outside to watch her.

99
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:33,270
Without my order,

100
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:35,920
no one is to bring Concubine Yu any food!

101
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,430
Concubine Yu was beside herself with rage,

102
00:05:37,430 --> 00:05:38,960
and what she said afterward

103
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:41,230
grew more and more incoherent.

104
00:05:42,390 --> 00:05:43,230
Heartless!

105
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:44,360
Without my abilities,

106
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,020
you, Xiahou Dan, are nothing!

107
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:48,830
We servants were terrified.

108
00:05:49,310 --> 00:05:50,680
She actually dared to defy His Majesty

109
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:52,480
and even called him by his personal name.

110
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,310
No one had ever seen such a scene before.

111
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:55,770
How did His Majesty react?

112
00:05:56,159 --> 00:05:58,360
Naturally, His Majesty flew into a rage

113
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,680
and immediately stripped Concubine Yu
of her title.

114
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,070
I see.

115
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,890
Go and receive your reward.

116
00:06:05,630 --> 00:06:07,090
Thank you, Your Highness.

117
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:14,160
Gentlemen,

118
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,410
what do you make of this matter?

119
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:18,610
Your Highness,

120
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:22,480
Consort Shu's family and the Yu family

121
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,750
had long been at odds.

122
00:06:25,870 --> 00:06:27,160
After Concubine Yu gained favor,

123
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:29,270
she kept Consort Shu
thoroughly suppressed.

124
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:31,400
Now that Minister Yu has been demoted,

125
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:34,360
Consort Shu's family is indeed
plotting in secret

126
00:06:34,510 --> 00:06:36,510
to poison him on his way to exile

127
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,680
and eliminate Minister Yu for good.

128
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:43,040
Using maid Mei to eliminate Consort Shu

129
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:47,130
would benefit Concubine Yu
whether it succeeded or failed—

130
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:50,640
a perfect two-birds-with-one-stone scheme.

131
00:06:51,270 --> 00:06:52,130
Your Highness,

132
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,190
I think

133
00:06:53,390 --> 00:06:55,590
this woman is not to be underestimated.

134
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:58,120
But there's one thing I don't understand

135
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:00,800
which feels somewhat suspicious.

136
00:07:01,430 --> 00:07:01,830
Speak.

137
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:04,640
Consort Shu's family acts in secret

138
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:06,920
and hasn't yet made their move,

139
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:09,750
while the Yu family remains
completely unaware.

140
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:10,920
Even we officials

141
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:14,080
only uncovered it
after considerable effort.

142
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:19,030
How could Consort Yu,
secluded deep in the palace,

143
00:07:19,490 --> 00:07:21,630
know about future events?

144
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,440
She couldn't have had

145
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:25,720
foresight, could she?

146
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:27,230
Nonsense.

147
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:34,710
This is getting more and more interesting.

148
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,409
Gentlemen, please have mercy.

149
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:45,620
[Office of Drums and Bells]

150
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:41,070
Please give me some food.

151
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:42,680
Buddy.

152
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:44,830
Buddy, look at me!

153
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:48,550
Buddy, please pass a word for me—

154
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:50,360
tell them Wanyin did nothing wrong.

155
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,890
I really did nothing wrong.

156
00:07:56,580 --> 00:07:58,390
Why is this door even harder than stone?

157
00:07:58,390 --> 00:07:59,320
It hurts so much.

158
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,700
You guys...

159
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:21,830
Your Highness.

160
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:22,190
Your Highness.

161
00:08:22,190 --> 00:08:23,050
Your Highness.

162
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,000
Hello.

163
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:32,880
Why are you here?

164
00:08:35,789 --> 00:08:37,669
I just dug a tunnel,
which is narrow and cramped.

165
00:08:37,669 --> 00:08:39,390
Took me forever to crawl through.

166
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:40,289
I wanted to ask you,

167
00:08:40,289 --> 00:08:42,090
what would you like to eat later?

168
00:08:42,700 --> 00:08:44,960
What could there be to eat
in the Cold Palace?

169
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,420
Hotpot?

170
00:08:46,550 --> 00:08:48,320
Why are you so obsessed with hotpot?

171
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:50,320
Aren't you the one who loves hotpot?

172
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,340
Nine-grid pot?

173
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:56,990
I'd rather have a yin-yang pot.

174
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,000
I knew it.

175
00:08:58,590 --> 00:09:00,630
With some chilled mung bean sweet soup.

176
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:01,420
All set!

177
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:07,420
This Cold Palace isn't so bad
once you tidy it up, right?

178
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:10,210
Maybe we should just move in here
for good.

179
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:12,990
Nonsense.

180
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,570
This used to be a storage room
for the music bureau.

181
00:09:23,570 --> 00:09:25,370
There's all sorts of stuff here.

182
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:26,730
But there's no pot.

183
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:27,650
Says who?

184
00:09:33,950 --> 00:09:35,230
Crawling through that tunnel

185
00:09:35,230 --> 00:09:37,720
with this pot on my back
was truly exhausting.

186
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,650
That's nothing.

187
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:40,480
I was carrying a table, okay?

188
00:09:41,770 --> 00:09:42,970
You're the real hero.

189
00:09:48,590 --> 00:09:50,360
What's the latest news outside?

190
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:52,440
The commander of the Imperial Guards
got drunk last night

191
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:54,100
and drowned in the lotus pond.

192
00:09:54,270 --> 00:09:55,240
It was Prince Duan's doing.

193
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,550
He's following Xu Yao's plan,
gradually eroding

194
00:09:56,550 --> 00:09:58,910
the Empress Dowager's faction's power
step by step.

195
00:09:58,910 --> 00:09:59,510
Just wait—

196
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,850
the court is going to get lively again.

197
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,900
But there's one more problem.

198
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,480
Ever since you confined me to
the Cold Palace,

199
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:12,390
Prince Duan has been sending letters
frequently, trying to win me over.

200
00:10:12,390 --> 00:10:13,360
He still hasn't given up on

201
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,690
finding out who the expert
by your side is.

202
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:17,590
Here, Your Highness.

203
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,460
Have some tripe.

204
00:10:18,460 --> 00:10:19,920
It's okay. Help yourself.

205
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:21,010
That's omasum.

206
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:22,430
This is tripe.

207
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,450
They taste similar.

208
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:35,480
Right.

209
00:10:38,260 --> 00:10:39,840
Since they taste similar,

210
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,280
when he wants tripe,

211
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:45,800
I can just give him omasum instead.

212
00:10:47,730 --> 00:10:48,880
So you mean

213
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,520
a bait and switch?

214
00:10:50,540 --> 00:10:51,920
Exactly—a classic decoy maneuver.

215
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:53,620
There's a secret guard
by the Empress Dowager's side

216
00:10:53,620 --> 00:10:54,880
with a scar on his face.

217
00:10:55,050 --> 00:10:56,980
And Mr. Bei knows the Disguise Art.

218
00:10:57,080 --> 00:11:00,540
-What a coincidence, isn't it?
-What a coincidence, isn't it?

219
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:01,380
Are you two

220
00:11:01,750 --> 00:11:02,950
speaking in riddles?

221
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:04,390
I don't understand a single word.

222
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:05,390
You're not supposed to.

223
00:11:05,390 --> 00:11:06,230
Just eat.

224
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:07,330
Come on.

225
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,910
I have a plan.

226
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:13,320
His Majesty is wary of me...

227
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:14,800
That's right.

228
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:15,480
Yet he

229
00:11:16,390 --> 00:11:18,590
dreads anyone else gaining my support,

230
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:22,250
so he's kept me imprisoned
the Cold Palace all this time.

231
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,840
These hopeless, miserable days...

232
00:11:28,030 --> 00:11:30,440
Are truly unbearable.

233
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,810
Hearing of your mistreatment,

234
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,240
my heart is aflame with worry

235
00:11:35,020 --> 00:11:36,470
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

236
00:11:36,490 --> 00:11:38,160
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

237
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:38,090
and I'm deeply concerned.

238
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,240
I only hope that you, Wanyin,

239
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:39,750
♪ Incredible ♪

240
00:11:39,690 --> 00:11:40,870
will keep yourself safe,

241
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,300
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

242
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:42,670
so that you can have a chance
to plan for the future.

243
00:11:41,850 --> 00:11:42,790
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

244
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,560
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

245
00:11:44,930 --> 00:11:46,090
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

246
00:11:45,030 --> 00:11:45,890
Your Highness,

247
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:47,620
if you truly care for me,

248
00:11:46,530 --> 00:11:47,900
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

249
00:11:48,170 --> 00:11:50,950
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

250
00:11:48,630 --> 00:11:50,690
I'll certainly do my best to help you.

251
00:11:51,290 --> 00:11:52,880
♪ From day to night ♪

252
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:54,750
But royal favor is so fleeting.

253
00:11:53,020 --> 00:11:54,450
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

254
00:11:54,540 --> 00:11:56,060
♪ From the present to the past ♪

255
00:11:56,210 --> 00:11:57,340
♪ It's always you ♪

256
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,830
Your Highness, how are you different

257
00:11:57,830 --> 00:11:59,330
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

258
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,840
from His Majesty?

259
00:11:59,350 --> 00:12:00,930
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

260
00:12:00,950 --> 00:12:03,840
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

261
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:07,260
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

262
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:09,220
♪ With you ♪

263
00:12:09,730 --> 00:12:12,040
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

264
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:12,440
It looks really like you.

265
00:12:12,090 --> 00:12:13,650
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

266
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:13,850
[If Your Highness truly cares for me,
I'll certainly do my best to help you.]

267
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,670
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

268
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:14,640
[But royal favor is so fleeting.
Your Highness, how are you different]

269
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:15,190
[from His Majesty?]

270
00:12:15,610 --> 00:12:16,690
There are many differences, of course.

271
00:12:16,170 --> 00:12:18,520
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

272
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:19,270
I only wish that one day,

273
00:12:18,570 --> 00:12:20,080
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

274
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,390
I could enjoy the Lantern Festival lights

275
00:12:20,100 --> 00:12:22,120
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

276
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:24,390
amid the splendor of fireworks
with you, Wanyin.

277
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:26,590
The sooner you help me succeed, Wanyin,

278
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:29,150
the sooner I can rescue you
from this peril.

279
00:12:32,590 --> 00:12:34,020
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

280
00:12:34,180 --> 00:12:35,840
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

281
00:12:34,270 --> 00:12:35,080
I'm so hungry.

282
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:39,080
Please give me more food.

283
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:41,630
I'm starving.

284
00:12:48,990 --> 00:12:50,210
♪ Incredible ♪

285
00:12:50,590 --> 00:12:51,770
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

286
00:12:52,190 --> 00:12:53,220
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

287
00:12:53,300 --> 00:12:54,950
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

288
00:12:55,290 --> 00:12:56,490
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

289
00:12:56,960 --> 00:12:58,190
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

290
00:12:58,540 --> 00:13:01,400
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

291
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:02,440
Pie in the sky?

292
00:13:01,650 --> 00:13:03,320
♪ From day to night ♪

293
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:04,930
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

294
00:13:04,990 --> 00:13:06,540
♪ From the present to the past ♪

295
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:06,520
In that case,

296
00:13:06,610 --> 00:13:07,720
♪ It's always you ♪

297
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,440
I'm willing to help with all my strength.

298
00:13:08,270 --> 00:13:09,700
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

299
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:11,770
I've already identified the expert
by His Majesty's side

300
00:13:09,770 --> 00:13:11,290
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

301
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:14,260
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

302
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:14,120
that Your Highness mentioned.

303
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:17,670
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

304
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:19,750
♪ With you ♪

305
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:22,540
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

306
00:13:22,630 --> 00:13:24,130
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

307
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:26,100
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

308
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:28,900
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

309
00:13:28,930 --> 00:13:30,560
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

310
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:32,510
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

311
00:13:42,930 --> 00:13:44,520
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

312
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:46,170
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

313
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,400
You blocked it just now.

314
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,910
♪ The wind is blowing gently ♪

315
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:47,930
You shouldn't have blocked that last move.

316
00:13:47,930 --> 00:13:49,210
♪ Bringing news ♪

317
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:49,120
Did I?

318
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:50,880
♪ About your whereabouts ♪

319
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:50,290
Yes, you did.

320
00:13:50,790 --> 00:13:52,480
You must know all the moves by heart.

321
00:13:50,950 --> 00:13:52,560
♪ Guiding me far away ♪

322
00:13:52,930 --> 00:13:54,100
♪ I carefully ♪

323
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:53,790
Instinct.

324
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:54,510
It was out of instinct.

325
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:55,880
♪ Collect time ♪

326
00:13:55,030 --> 00:13:56,080
I'm just too good.

327
00:13:56,040 --> 00:13:57,860
♪ I'll hide it well ♪

328
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:57,770
It's lonely at the top.

329
00:13:58,080 --> 00:14:00,560
♪ The secret of meeting you ♪

330
00:13:58,590 --> 00:14:00,790
How about I come up
and keep you company?

331
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:05,550
Why hasn't Her Highness
finished cutting the melon yet?

332
00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:06,810
I'll go eat some melon.

333
00:14:07,670 --> 00:14:08,960
I've just warmed up.

334
00:14:08,570 --> 00:14:10,080
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

335
00:14:10,140 --> 00:14:11,850
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

336
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:11,430
Dan.

337
00:14:13,630 --> 00:14:14,890
Come practice with me.

338
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:34,370
Your Highness.

339
00:14:37,030 --> 00:14:37,960
Have some melon.

340
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,320
Why did you stop practicing?

341
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:44,960
Just those few moves—

342
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,840
I've mastered them long ago.

343
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,240
You've both worked hard.

344
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,130
We just give orders,

345
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:50,960
and you run yourselves ragged.

346
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:51,760
It's nothing—

347
00:14:52,150 --> 00:14:53,410
not worth mentioning.

348
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,500
After this matter is settled,

349
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,020
I'll have to leave.

350
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,080
So soon?

351
00:15:05,510 --> 00:15:08,270
Weren't you ordered by your master
to protect His Majesty?

352
00:15:08,270 --> 00:15:09,960
But with Prince Duan watching,

353
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:11,960
I can't appear by your side anymore.

354
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:13,690
That's true.

355
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:17,980
So, have you decided where you want to go?

356
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:20,570
His Majesty has given me another task.

357
00:15:20,790 --> 00:15:21,440
What task?

358
00:15:23,510 --> 00:15:24,370
I can't say yet.

359
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:26,280
You'll know when the time comes.

360
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:28,350
So there's a secret mission?

361
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:34,610
Your Highness.

362
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:40,850
Would you like to leave with me?

363
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:41,600
What?

364
00:15:44,330 --> 00:15:45,960
From the first time I saw you,

365
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:48,960
I knew you were a skylark
meant for the open sky,

366
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:51,090
not to be trapped within palace walls.

367
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:53,320
As long as you say yes,

368
00:15:53,750 --> 00:15:54,680
I'll take care of

369
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:56,030
persuading His Majesty.

370
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:57,320
What are you talking about?

371
00:15:57,320 --> 00:15:59,360
Trying to steal me
right under His Majesty's nose?

372
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,090
I'm serious.

373
00:16:00,630 --> 00:16:01,430
I have a reason

374
00:16:01,920 --> 00:16:03,120
he'll have to accept.

375
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:04,120
Stop it.

376
00:16:04,510 --> 00:16:05,230
Anyway,

377
00:16:05,390 --> 00:16:07,050
thank you for telling me this.

378
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:10,370
You don't have to give me an answer
right away.

379
00:16:10,510 --> 00:16:11,200
Please.

380
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:13,790
Bai,

381
00:16:14,670 --> 00:16:16,070
a fine young hero like you

382
00:16:16,270 --> 00:16:19,130
will surely have a beauty by your side
in the future.

383
00:16:23,550 --> 00:16:24,010
Then...

384
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:26,910
If it weren't with me,

385
00:16:28,090 --> 00:16:30,350
would you want to go out
and see the world?

386
00:16:31,820 --> 00:16:32,680
Your Highness.

387
00:16:34,230 --> 00:16:35,290
What I want to say is

388
00:16:36,070 --> 00:16:37,530
that beyond this capital,

389
00:16:38,060 --> 00:16:39,660
there's a whole other world.

390
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:41,440
Once you step beyond these palace walls,

391
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,110
you can

392
00:16:42,510 --> 00:16:44,970
gallop freely on horseback, unrestrained.

393
00:16:45,870 --> 00:16:46,960
Wouldn't a life like that

394
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:47,960
be exhilarating?

395
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:52,300
Your Highness.

396
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,530
Think it over for yourself.

397
00:16:58,510 --> 00:17:00,440
Since you've come into this world,

398
00:17:01,090 --> 00:17:02,750
what is it that you truly want?

399
00:17:18,750 --> 00:17:20,400
-In my dream, I saw that
-"In my dream, I saw that

400
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:22,200
-on the eighth day of October,
-on the eighth day of October,

401
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:24,750
-the expert rode alone to Zhangtai,
-the expert rode alone to Zhangtai..."

402
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:26,410
to that entertainment house.

403
00:17:27,030 --> 00:17:28,960
In front of him was a high platform,

404
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,530
behind him a crescent moon,

405
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:33,580
and it looked like
he was watching a variety act.

406
00:17:35,150 --> 00:17:37,270
The eighth day of October is tomorrow.

407
00:17:37,270 --> 00:17:39,530
Do you believe her words, Your Highness?

408
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:43,370
Not completely, of course.

409
00:17:44,590 --> 00:17:45,240
So...

410
00:17:54,590 --> 00:17:55,920
Make the arrangements—

411
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,770
I'll pay a visit to the palace tonight.

412
00:17:59,430 --> 00:17:59,850
Yes.

413
00:18:22,790 --> 00:18:23,320
Yong'er.

414
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,690
Greetings, Your Highness.

415
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:28,550
You've just recovered from
a serious illness

416
00:18:28,550 --> 00:18:30,480
and recently experienced a shock.

417
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:33,030
No need for formalities between us.

418
00:18:33,030 --> 00:18:34,920
Thank you for your concern, Your Highness.

419
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:35,880
I'm fine now.

420
00:18:38,270 --> 00:18:42,310
Zhao Wucheng has successfully taken over
as commander of the Imperial Guards.

421
00:18:42,310 --> 00:18:45,370
I must thank you
for your excellent strategy, Yong'er.

422
00:18:46,270 --> 00:18:48,830
However, there's another
troublesome matter now.

423
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:51,690
A skilled expert has appeared
by the Emperor's side

424
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:54,130
and has put me in danger several times.

425
00:18:55,200 --> 00:18:56,860
Yong'er, do you know anything

426
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:58,020
about this matter?

427
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:02,000
Is he referring to Bei Zhou,
the supreme martial artist

428
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:05,000
who has deep connections with the Emperor
in the book?

429
00:19:06,110 --> 00:19:08,920
But I remember
he should appear much later.

430
00:19:11,030 --> 00:19:13,110
I vaguely recall seeing
glimpses of him in my dreams.

431
00:19:13,110 --> 00:19:14,840
This person does seem to exist.

432
00:19:19,550 --> 00:19:20,610
So, Your Highness,

433
00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:23,110
is this why you've come to see me?

434
00:19:30,830 --> 00:19:32,560
Are you angry with me, Yong'er?

435
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:37,030
As a mere palace consort,

436
00:19:38,720 --> 00:19:41,520
what right do I have to be angry with
Your Highness?

437
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:44,400
I'm merely lamenting my own fate.

438
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:48,960
Your Highness, look at the flowers
in this flower house.

439
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:50,220
Beautiful as they are,

440
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:53,050
they're confined to this small space.

441
00:19:53,310 --> 00:19:54,070
Tell me,

442
00:19:55,350 --> 00:19:57,750
besides waiting for others to admire them,

443
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:00,990
what else can they do?

444
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:09,640
Yong'er.

445
00:20:10,590 --> 00:20:11,990
Perhaps in others' eyes,

446
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:14,590
I'm a prince close to the people,

447
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:17,790
a valiant general,

448
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:21,420
someone expected to become a wise ruler.

449
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,930
But no one actually cares about

450
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:28,070
what kind of person I truly am

451
00:20:32,070 --> 00:20:33,550
deep down.

452
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:43,210
Within these palace walls,

453
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:48,310
I endured the darkest days of my life—

454
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:52,200
trampled,

455
00:20:53,830 --> 00:20:54,680
humiliated,

456
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:58,110
whipped—

457
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:04,030
simply because my mother

458
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:09,590
was a lowlife in this palace.

459
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:14,070
I guess she was favored once,

460
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:17,110
but before long,

461
00:21:18,540 --> 00:21:21,400
she was trampled by
someone even more favored

462
00:21:25,440 --> 00:21:28,570
and became a wronged soul
lingering in this dark palace.

463
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:35,060
So no one understands better than I do

464
00:21:37,350 --> 00:21:38,550
what this vast palace

465
00:21:40,280 --> 00:21:42,030
means for a woman.

466
00:21:45,350 --> 00:21:47,350
And no one is more desperate than I am

467
00:21:47,750 --> 00:21:51,010
to take her out of this sea of suffering
as soon as possible,

468
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:55,180
to be together for all lifetimes to come.

469
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:59,680
But I don't have that ability right now.

470
00:22:01,110 --> 00:22:03,440
Perhaps I shouldn't have approached you,

471
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,700
perhaps I'm not the right man for you,

472
00:22:09,310 --> 00:22:11,510
or perhaps from the very beginning,
I never should have...

473
00:22:11,510 --> 00:22:12,970
Your Highness, I'm sorry.

474
00:22:17,270 --> 00:22:18,600
I was being willful.

475
00:22:20,750 --> 00:22:22,750
I know Your Highness bears the world

476
00:22:25,150 --> 00:22:26,290
on your shoulders.

477
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:29,960
What is a little grievance on my part
compared to that?

478
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:17,000
Mr. Bei.

479
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:18,510
The dagger's finished?

480
00:23:18,510 --> 00:23:20,110
It wasn't difficult to make.

481
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:21,970
The credit goes to your design.

482
00:23:23,350 --> 00:23:23,680
Look.

483
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:30,890
Impressive.

484
00:23:32,830 --> 00:23:34,680
As soon as tonight's operation is over,

485
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:35,830
I'll help Bai leave.

486
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:37,510
In such a hurry?

487
00:23:38,110 --> 00:23:40,110
Dan's arrangements won't be wrong.

488
00:23:43,310 --> 00:23:45,240
Then I'll go say goodbye to him now.

489
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:56,300
Last night when I observed the stars,

490
00:23:56,750 --> 00:23:58,010
I noticed those 5 stars

491
00:23:58,030 --> 00:23:59,160
were about to align.

492
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:00,340
So?

493
00:24:03,240 --> 00:24:05,700
Master's divinations are always accurate,

494
00:24:05,750 --> 00:24:08,150
and he asked me to pass along
one more thing:

495
00:24:11,820 --> 00:24:13,400
your meeting with each other

496
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:15,320
may not be a blessing after all.

497
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:19,830
You're just making this up, aren't you?

498
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:22,230
I wouldn't dare joke about Master's words.

499
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:25,790
Let her leave sooner—

500
00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:27,410
maybe you both can survive.

501
00:24:28,110 --> 00:24:29,910
If you covet Wanyin, just say so.

502
00:24:30,110 --> 00:24:31,160
I mean well.

503
00:24:33,370 --> 00:24:35,370
Even if you won't think of yourself,

504
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,080
at least think of her.

505
00:24:39,030 --> 00:24:40,810
What does it matter
that you're the Emperor?

506
00:24:40,810 --> 00:24:41,870
Can you protect her

507
00:24:42,200 --> 00:24:43,530
from being mistreated?

508
00:24:44,590 --> 00:24:45,320
That I can do.

509
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:51,370
Then can you promise

510
00:24:51,590 --> 00:24:53,270
to love only her—to take
just this one ladle from the vast waters?

511
00:24:53,270 --> 00:24:54,270
That's also easy.

512
00:24:57,480 --> 00:24:58,010
Alright.

513
00:25:02,070 --> 00:25:02,510
Fine.

514
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:05,540
Even if you can do all that you say,

515
00:25:05,790 --> 00:25:07,110
she'll still be a bird in a cage,

516
00:25:07,110 --> 00:25:09,480
never able to roam freely and happily
in this world.

517
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:09,960
Bai.

518
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:15,180
The world isn't just for roaming freely.

519
00:25:16,110 --> 00:25:17,570
She has her own ambitions.

520
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:23,040
You only see her as a little bird

521
00:25:23,510 --> 00:25:24,910
that needs to be set free,

522
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:26,550
but you fail to see

523
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:29,800
how upright and noble she is—

524
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:31,780
radiant as the sun,

525
00:25:33,750 --> 00:25:35,610
able to light up the vast blue sky.

526
00:25:41,030 --> 00:25:41,890
Your Highness.

527
00:25:42,830 --> 00:25:44,360
Think it over for yourself.

528
00:25:45,330 --> 00:25:47,260
Since you've come into this world,

529
00:25:47,310 --> 00:25:48,790
what is it that you truly want?

530
00:25:48,790 --> 00:25:51,160
That kind of life would be wonderful,
of course.

531
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:53,290
But I have more important things to do.

532
00:25:53,950 --> 00:25:55,010
Bai, you know what?

533
00:25:55,480 --> 00:25:56,640
Back in my hometown,

534
00:25:57,420 --> 00:25:58,920
we liked to use the term
"corporate slaves"

535
00:25:58,920 --> 00:26:00,250
to describe ourselves,

536
00:26:01,510 --> 00:26:02,270
as if

537
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:04,680
we were all just slaves—

538
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:07,170
blindfolded and driven by others,

539
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:10,220
doing meaningless things day after day.

540
00:26:11,490 --> 00:26:12,750
But now I have a chance.

541
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:15,460
When I'm able to do more for this world

542
00:26:15,550 --> 00:26:17,240
and for more people,

543
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:21,930
I no longer want to live
just for my own happiness.

544
00:26:23,510 --> 00:26:25,540
The Polaris restores the light in the sky.

545
00:26:25,540 --> 00:26:27,470
A dark omen of royal blood and ruin;

546
00:26:27,830 --> 00:26:29,960
fortune and calamity hang by a thread.

547
00:26:30,350 --> 00:26:31,480
Five stars align,

548
00:26:30,630 --> 00:26:34,350
[The Nameless,
a master beyond the worldly realm]

549
00:26:32,790 --> 00:26:34,920
amidst despair, great fortune rises.

550
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:43,330
These two people are entangled
in many karmic connections.

551
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:45,080
Their past lives

552
00:26:48,750 --> 00:26:50,840
are not in this mortal realm.

553
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:54,930
So annoying.

554
00:26:56,310 --> 00:26:57,570
I'll go pack my things.

555
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:59,320
But you're right, actually.

556
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:01,500
It's truly hard for her

557
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:04,030
to feel happy here.

558
00:27:07,170 --> 00:27:09,230
If one day she fulfills her ambitions

559
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:10,650
and wishes to leave,

560
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:15,440
and I'm no longer around by then,

561
00:27:17,430 --> 00:27:18,690
take her away with you.

562
00:27:26,550 --> 00:27:27,810
Don't say such things.

563
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:30,640
Please, I'm begging you.

564
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:58,140
Here, Mr. Li. There are still seats here.

565
00:27:58,340 --> 00:27:59,470
Let's go take a look.

566
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:01,720
This way, sir.

567
00:28:03,030 --> 00:28:05,310
Gentlemen, thank you for
honoring us today

568
00:28:05,310 --> 00:28:06,590
with your generous tips.

569
00:28:06,590 --> 00:28:08,350
I guarantee you'll be satisfied with

570
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:09,830
our variety acts today.

571
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:11,240
Fill the wine,

572
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:12,680
pour the tea,

573
00:28:13,550 --> 00:28:15,070
and let the music begin!

574
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,700
Alright, alright.

575
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:20,640
Why are you standing here?
Please go upstairs.

576
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,030
Come on.

577
00:28:21,030 --> 00:28:21,560
Alright.

578
00:28:25,830 --> 00:28:26,310
Sir.

579
00:28:27,590 --> 00:28:28,990
What took you so long?

580
00:28:29,110 --> 00:28:30,640
We've been waiting for you.

581
00:28:30,970 --> 00:28:32,700
Come on, have a seat over there.

582
00:28:33,900 --> 00:28:35,320
No rush,

583
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:36,350
no rush.

584
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:40,060
Today, we have a newly composed song

585
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:41,510
called "The Fish Basket Melody."

586
00:28:41,510 --> 00:28:43,240
The new girls are sweet-tongued as honey—

587
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:45,500
miss them now and you'll regret it later.

588
00:28:48,480 --> 00:28:50,540
Please, come in—upstairs, this way.

589
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:01,500
My Lord, they're here.

590
00:29:02,240 --> 00:29:03,370
Proceed as planned.

591
00:29:03,590 --> 00:29:03,920
Yes.

592
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:10,380
Trust me, you won't regret it.

593
00:29:12,680 --> 00:29:14,440
Young master, please drink more.

594
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:14,970
Alright.

595
00:29:21,720 --> 00:29:23,480
Sir, do you need anything?

596
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:28,620
Hey,

597
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,830
let's talk things through.

598
00:29:32,310 --> 00:29:33,900
Send our people up

599
00:29:34,400 --> 00:29:36,200
to perform the next variety act.

600
00:29:36,310 --> 00:29:38,640
Don't alarm the audience below the stage.

601
00:29:41,920 --> 00:29:44,080
Sir, drink less next time, alright?

602
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:57,640
Bravo!

603
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:58,200
Bravo!

604
00:30:00,440 --> 00:30:01,050
How nice!

605
00:30:10,030 --> 00:30:11,310
Bravo!

606
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:13,240
Bravo!

607
00:30:13,550 --> 00:30:14,070
Bravo!

608
00:30:14,400 --> 00:30:15,000
Bravo!

609
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:16,160
They're really skilled.

610
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:17,400
Yes, truly impressive.

611
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,070
Bravo!

612
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:19,470
This is truly wonderful.

613
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:21,560
-Bravo!
-Truly impressive.

614
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:33,830
Bravo! Bravo!

615
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:42,830
Such martial skills.

616
00:30:42,830 --> 00:30:43,640
This is truly impressive!

617
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:44,480
Really amazing!

618
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:46,310
His skills are truly impressive.

619
00:30:46,310 --> 00:30:47,310
-Bravo!
-Bravo!

620
00:30:49,480 --> 00:30:50,210
Look at that!

621
00:30:52,350 --> 00:30:52,750
Bravo!

622
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:58,770
Murder!

623
00:31:03,110 --> 00:31:05,090
[Prince Duan's Mansion]

624
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:13,820
Your Highness.

625
00:31:15,350 --> 00:31:16,080
How did it go?

626
00:31:17,750 --> 00:31:19,030
There's both good news

627
00:31:19,590 --> 00:31:20,790
and bad news.

628
00:31:21,310 --> 00:31:23,110
Stop keeping us in suspense.
Just tell us the result.

629
00:31:23,110 --> 00:31:23,550
Say it.

630
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:26,090
The plan succeeded.

631
00:31:28,110 --> 00:31:28,840
However,

632
00:31:30,510 --> 00:31:32,040
all the assassins sent

633
00:31:32,550 --> 00:31:33,720
were wiped out.

634
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:35,620
Then...

635
00:31:36,310 --> 00:31:36,770
This...

636
00:31:38,310 --> 00:31:39,000
Continue.

637
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:42,110
As soon as the fight broke out,

638
00:31:42,110 --> 00:31:43,880
the audience scattered in all directions,

639
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:46,210
and the place descended into total chaos.

640
00:31:46,270 --> 00:31:47,510
That fellow was surrounded

641
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:49,330
on all sides by the assassins,

642
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:53,740
yet with a single swift move, he slipped
through a gap in their encirclement,

643
00:31:55,830 --> 00:31:57,560
which was truly unbelievable.

644
00:31:57,830 --> 00:31:59,540
He was clearly stabbed once,

645
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:02,690
but it didn't seem to affect him
in the slightest.

646
00:32:02,790 --> 00:32:03,960
He kept fighting,

647
00:32:05,990 --> 00:32:07,870
charging left and right.

648
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:08,790
Then came

649
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:10,210
a second blow,

650
00:32:10,550 --> 00:32:11,600
and then a third.

651
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:13,350
Each strike looked fatal,

652
00:32:13,350 --> 00:32:15,610
blades flashing with blood everywhere—

653
00:32:17,110 --> 00:32:21,210
yet he still showed no sign of faltering,
as if nothing were wrong.

654
00:32:35,720 --> 00:32:38,310
Only after he had killed the last assassin

655
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:41,300
did he let out a long peal of laughter,
"hahaha,"

656
00:32:42,550 --> 00:32:44,150
and then finally collapsed.

657
00:32:48,350 --> 00:32:49,830
Why are you repeating the laughter?

658
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:52,230
You're here to report,
not to tell stories.

659
00:32:52,790 --> 00:32:53,650
Your Highness.

660
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:55,920
What I just said

661
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:58,510
wasn't exaggerated at all.

662
00:33:02,240 --> 00:33:03,840
Where's that expert's body?

663
00:33:04,750 --> 00:33:05,720
After he died,

664
00:33:06,110 --> 00:33:08,640
the officers ordered
the brothel keepers to clean up the scene

665
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:10,400
and wipe away all the bloodstains.

666
00:33:10,400 --> 00:33:10,720
My Lord.

667
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:13,400
-I sent someone to buy the body.
-My Lord, the body is here.

668
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:15,130
And we confirmed his identity.

669
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:16,970
Who is he?

670
00:33:17,720 --> 00:33:20,560
Based on the body and his belongings,

671
00:33:20,750 --> 00:33:23,680
he was a trusted secret guard
of the Empress Dowager.

672
00:33:26,270 --> 00:33:27,470
The Empress Dowager?

673
00:33:28,490 --> 00:33:30,880
Extremely ruthless
with exceptional skills,

674
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:32,540
with a long scar on his face.

675
00:33:33,270 --> 00:33:34,070
He was someone

676
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:38,070
we were specifically
on guard against before.

677
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:41,600
So you're saying the Empress Dowager's man

678
00:33:42,160 --> 00:33:43,820
was protecting the Emperor?

679
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:47,340
This...

680
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:48,920
I never expected

681
00:33:48,960 --> 00:33:51,160
things would turn out like this, either.

682
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,760
Why would the Empress Dowager

683
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:55,140
suddenly show goodwill to the Emperor?

684
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,860
This is too bizarre.

685
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:58,440
A-Absolutely impossible.

686
00:33:58,440 --> 00:33:59,440
Have you forgotten

687
00:33:59,440 --> 00:34:01,030
how fiercely they fought

688
00:34:01,030 --> 00:34:03,000
over the Salt-for-Services Policy?

689
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:04,110
That was an intense confrontation

690
00:34:04,110 --> 00:34:06,000
known to everyone at court.

691
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:06,960
How could they suddenly...

692
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:08,000
Or perhaps

693
00:34:09,100 --> 00:34:12,500
he was a spy the Empress Dowager
placed at the Emperor's side.

694
00:34:13,699 --> 00:34:14,159
Then...

695
00:34:15,170 --> 00:34:17,070
Then wouldn't we have killed
the wrong person

696
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:18,550
and actually helped the Emperor

697
00:34:18,550 --> 00:34:19,679
eliminate a threat?

698
00:34:23,510 --> 00:34:25,969
Gentlemen, there's no need
to overthink it.

699
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:28,639
Eliminating someone of such special status

700
00:34:28,639 --> 00:34:30,440
actually gives us peace of mind.

701
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:34,219
At this point, the two of them
are both spent forces.

702
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:36,730
With the court rife with intrigue,

703
00:34:37,590 --> 00:34:38,449
replacing them

704
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,960
is only a matter of time.

705
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:43,960
Your Highness is wise.

706
00:34:50,120 --> 00:34:52,000
[Zhang San's Diary]

707
00:34:52,070 --> 00:34:53,360
I heard

708
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:56,150
you've been coming to the library
every few days.

709
00:34:56,710 --> 00:34:59,190
I thought you were diligently studying.

710
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:00,860
I didn't expect

711
00:35:01,510 --> 00:35:04,110
you'd be so fond of
these plants and flowers.

712
00:35:05,710 --> 00:35:06,750
Your Majesty,

713
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:07,910
I

714
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:10,550
am not wasting time on frivolous pursuits.

715
00:35:10,550 --> 00:35:11,580
I-I'm just...

716
00:35:12,590 --> 00:35:13,150
Just...

717
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:17,330
Just what?

718
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:18,630
This...

719
00:35:18,630 --> 00:35:19,430
Your Majesty.

720
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:20,880
I know I was wrong.

721
00:35:21,150 --> 00:35:22,150
I know I was wrong.

722
00:35:24,960 --> 00:35:26,090
Silly kid.

723
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:28,290
You've done nothing wrong.

724
00:35:30,260 --> 00:35:32,340
I haven't blamed you for anything.

725
00:35:32,590 --> 00:35:34,390
There's no need to be so nervous.

726
00:35:35,670 --> 00:35:39,190
[SOS]

727
00:35:36,190 --> 00:35:37,510
The late Empress Dowager

728
00:35:37,510 --> 00:35:38,710
once held you

729
00:35:39,510 --> 00:35:40,760
in very high regard.

730
00:35:42,070 --> 00:35:46,110
It's just that she was overly strict
in disciplining you.

731
00:35:47,630 --> 00:35:48,760
I, on the other hand,

732
00:35:49,150 --> 00:35:50,610
have no children of my own.

733
00:35:51,630 --> 00:35:52,260
Why don't

734
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:54,230
you become

735
00:35:54,710 --> 00:35:56,190
my child instead?

736
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:02,970
I'm different from
the late Empress Dowager.

737
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:05,110
I only hope that you, Crown Prince,

738
00:36:05,110 --> 00:36:07,470
can grow up happily.

739
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:10,280
You don't have to do things
you don't like.

740
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:11,860
If you don't want to study,

741
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:12,990
then don't.

742
00:36:13,150 --> 00:36:15,180
If you like these flowers and plants,

743
00:36:14,390 --> 00:36:21,340
[SOS]

744
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:17,000
then tend to them as you wish.

745
00:36:17,510 --> 00:36:18,320
You see,

746
00:36:18,550 --> 00:36:20,030
his gardening is

747
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:21,590
actually quite beautiful.

748
00:36:21,590 --> 00:36:22,850
Your Majesty is right.

749
00:36:24,510 --> 00:36:25,400
Your Majesty,

750
00:36:26,510 --> 00:36:27,310
do you mean it?

751
00:36:28,710 --> 00:36:29,810
When I speak,

752
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:31,520
I always mean what I say.

753
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:37,280
Thank you, Your Majesty.

754
00:36:39,710 --> 00:36:40,570
Your Highness,

755
00:36:40,890 --> 00:36:42,690
this is an incredible blessing!

756
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:44,550
Why are you still calling her
"Your Majesty?"

757
00:36:44,550 --> 00:36:46,070
You should change how you address her

758
00:36:46,070 --> 00:36:47,530
and call her "Mother" now.

759
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:50,920
I

760
00:36:51,670 --> 00:36:53,050
thank you, Mother.

761
00:36:58,320 --> 00:37:00,100
My dear son.

762
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,170
See,

763
00:37:01,550 --> 00:37:02,810
isn't this wonderful?

764
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:09,410
Look at these flowers.

765
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:10,710
They're truly exquisite.

766
00:37:10,710 --> 00:37:11,440
Yeah.

767
00:37:11,590 --> 00:37:13,320
And the color is beautiful too.

768
00:37:14,590 --> 00:37:15,990
Let's take a closer look.

769
00:37:16,340 --> 00:37:17,470
Don't go over there.

770
00:37:17,550 --> 00:37:18,480
Let's leave now.

771
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:20,450
Let's go.

772
00:37:21,110 --> 00:37:21,670
We don't want to be late.

773
00:37:21,670 --> 00:37:22,440
Just one look.

774
00:37:22,440 --> 00:37:24,500
Sister will be worried if we're late.

775
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:44,300
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness.

776
00:37:51,110 --> 00:37:52,700
The palace is so vast,

777
00:37:53,060 --> 00:37:54,840
yet His Highness spends every day
just admiring these Hydrangeas

778
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,440
and never seems to tire of it.

779
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:57,840
Exactly.

780
00:37:58,320 --> 00:37:59,880
You don't think he's possessed by
some flower spirit, do you?
